{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/key_feat.png?t=1720520604\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/real_time_tac.png?t=1720520604\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/steam_descr_1.gif?t=1720520604\" /><br>In Quest for Gold you control squads of knights and archers to defend your castle from attacking waves of Goblins. They will attack you with various weapons such as TNT throwers, flame-torches and even exploding barrels. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/relaxed_control.png?t=1720520604\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/steam_descr_2.gif?t=1720520604\" /><br>Your troops are grouped into squads of multiple units. This way you can easily position your troops to block the Goblins from reaching your castle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/strat_res.png?t=1720520604\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/extras/steam_descr_3.gif?t=1720520604\" /><br>Whenever you've defeated a Goblin wave you will be given a choice of strategic resources to use. Replace squad losses or build towers to prepare for the next wave.<br><br><i>Gold Rush! Expeditions are sent from all parts of the realm to new found lands where vast mines of gold have been discovered. The king has sent you on a quest to go to these lands and participate in the gold rush. Will you be able to mine the gold or will the Goblin threat prove too tough?</i>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428520/pa